bilingual.target: 用身份证证明你的身份。

bilingual.source: Someone might use the information to steal your identity.
bilingual.target: 有人可能会利用这些信息盗取你的身份。
有人丢失了一张身份证。

bilingual.source: And so I use a nonsense name for my net identity.
bilingual.target: 所以我用一个无意义的名字作为我的网络身份。

bilingual.source: "Maybe she robbed a bank in Korea and needs a new identity," a boy replied.
bilingual.target: “也许她在韩国抢了银行，需要一个新身份，”一个男孩回答。
我们需要查证他的身份。
我们需要核实你的身份。
他们正在核实他的身份。

list.abstract: 《Identity》是由Jin Nakamura作词，荘野ジュリ作曲，宫野真守演唱的歌曲，该歌曲收录于专辑《PASSAGE》中。
Identity，汉语意思为同一（性）; 一致；身份； 本身； 本体； 个性； 特性。另有同名音乐专辑和同名电影。还有数据库语言也会用到。

yingyinNormal.en: The rest of their identity is built around it, layer by layer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们其余的身份都是根据这个一层一层地构建的。

yingyinNormal.en: A smokescreen to conceal my true identity. My name is Khan.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是一个烟雾弹来掩盖我的真实身份，我的名字是可汗。

yingyinNormal.en: Relax, Harold. I'm just the nanny. My sixth new identity in two weeks.
yingyinNormal.zh: 放松，哈罗德，我只是保姆，我这两周的第六个新身份。

yingyinNormal.en: Given that we're tied to these very specific personas, your identity seems remarkably fluid.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们都被局限于特定的角色，你的身份却随时变化。

yingyinNormal.en: A precious few people know about your true identity. It would be unfortunate if we forgot.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没什么人知道你的真实身份，要是我们不小心忘了就惨了。

yingyinNormal.en: Your memories are woven into your identity. If I should unlock them now when you're conscious...
yingyinNormal.zh: 你的记忆与你的身份交织而成，如果我在你清醒的时候解锁...

yingyinNormal.en: Walls and guards, dogs and moats. Prince, the answer to the assassins' identity rests in your question.
yingyinNormal.zh: 城墙和侍卫，狗和护城河，王子，刺客的身份就隐藏在你的问题中。

yingyinNormal.en: Recruit former agents from other nations, supply them with a new identity and use them to surgically remove our enemies, both at home and abroad.
yingyinNormal.zh: 招募其他国家退役的特工，给他们新的身份，利用他们除掉我们国内外的敌人。

yingyinNormal.en: Witnesses are reporting that there was a quick succession of gunshots, four or five, a lone gunman whose identity we are still trying to determine.
yingyinNormal.zh: 目击者声称当时有连续好几声枪响，约有四五发，枪手是一个人，身份还未确认。

yingyinNormal.en: Your Honor, the identity of nurses at Indiana State is kept confidential so that it doesn't become known that they participated in an execution.
yingyinNormal.zh: 法官阁下，为了保护护士参与行刑任务的保密性，他们的身份在印第安纳州是不公开的。

yingyinNormal.en: What difference does it make? The whole point of a secret knock is to establish a non-verbal signal to verify the identity of one's co-conspirators.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有什么区别啊？设置敲门密码的所有意义就在于建立一种非语言信号，来验证某人的同行者身份的办法。

yingyinNormal.en: Made up a story. A new identity. This one, I took at a forest. For six months, they were friends. You work 25 hours on top of school?
yingyinNormal.zh: 他编了一个故事。一个新身份。这张，是我在森林里照的。那六个月里，他们是朋友。你放学后要打二十五个小时的工？

yingyinNormal.en: The bright lure of freedom diminishes your life's joy in a mad scramble for power, for identity.
yingyinNormal.zh: 自由的诱惑剥夺了你们生活中的快乐，你们疯狂地追求权势，追求地位。

yingyinNormal.en: It's a masquerade. You have to conceal your identity, but I do have something special planned for Nate tonight.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那可是化装舞会，你得把自己"藏"起来，但我今晚为内特做了特别的安排。

yingyinNormal.en: Huge Ackman? That's a ridiculous name! It doesn't even sound real! Only a coward would conceal his true identity, Arthur.
yingyinNormal.zh: 休了杰克妈？这名字太荒唐了！这听着都不像真名！只有懦夫才会隐姓埋名，亚瑟。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Night at the Museum: Secret of the Tomb》

yingyinNormal.en: Well, there are studies that suggest that many who go into the performing arts suffer from an external locus of identity.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有研究表明很多从事演艺事业的人都受外界认同的煎熬。

yingyinNormal.en: The identity of the next President of these United States is once again in the hands of a bunch of self-serving, money-hungry, boot-licking, power-seeking politicians who can be seduced or sucker punched or blackmailed into submission.
yingyinNormal.zh: 美国总统的宝座花落谁家决定权再次落到了这一帮自私自利，嗜财如命，阿谀谄媚，贪恋权势的政治家手里或者要挟就能让他们服从。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: the fact of being who or what a person or thing is

examination_example.sentence: Today the rapid growth of artificial intelligence (AI) raises fundamental questions: "What is intelligence, <highlight>identity</highlight>, or consciousness? What makes humans humans? "
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如今，人工智能的迅速发展引出了一些根本性的问题：“什么是智能、身份或意识？什么使人类成为人类？”

examination_example.sentence: Facebook promised that it would not link phone numbers to Facebook <highlight>identities</highlight>, but it broke the promise.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 脸书曾承诺，不会将电话号码与脸书的身份认证相关联，但是它违背了这一承诺。

examination_example.sentence: With or without permission, they straddle laws, jurisdictions and <highlight>identities</highlight> with ease.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 不管有没有许可，他们都可以轻易跨越法律、司法管辖区和身份。

sense_info_list.en: the characteristics determining who or what a person or thing is

examination_example.sentence: It is not that pink is intrinsically bad, though it may celebrate girlhood, it repeatedly and firmly fuses girls' <highlight>identity</highlight> to appearance.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 并不是说粉色本身不好，尽管也许粉色歌颂了少女时代，但是也只是反复并固化地将女孩的特质融入其外在形象。
